10:T405,{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"Movie","name":"Eyyvah Eyvah","description":"Hüseyin is a young man who lives with his grandfather and grandmother in a village in Thracian Turkey. The two great loves of his life are his clarinet and Müjgan, a nurse. Although Hüseyin is content with his life, with his music and dreams of Mügan, due to an unexpected development he leaves his village. He ends up in Istanbul where he finds support first in his clarinet and then in the friendship of the singer Firuzan. Firuzan is a popular nightclub performer who is eagerly working on an album as she leads a colorful but complicated life. When Firuzan meets Huseyin, the course of events gives away to a hilarious adventure.","image":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/cXRQLlxt7FMOySNQhXYRjTKjtEJ.jpg","datePublished":"2010-02-26","numberOfEpisodes":null,"countryOfOrigin":"TR","inLanguage":"tr","genre":["comedy film","Comedy",null],"aggregateRating":{"@type":"AggregateRating","ratingValue":6.4,"bestRating":10,"ratingCount":120}}5:[["$","script",null,{"type":"application/ld+json","dangerouslySetInnerHTML":{"__html":"$10"}}],["$","$L11",null,{"initialDrama":{"id":"0827aecd-f334-4076-a398-01a46acd4eeb","tmdb_id":48763,"imdb_id":"tt1594918","content_type":"movie","title":"Eyyvah Eyvah","original_title":"Eyyvah Eyvah","overview":"Hüseyin is a young man who lives with his grandfather and grandmother in a village in Thracian Turkey. The two great loves of his life are his clarinet and Müjgan, a nurse. Although Hüseyin is content with his life, with his music and dreams of Mügan, due to an unexpected development he leaves his village. He ends up in Istanbul where he finds support first in his clarinet and then in the friendship of the singer Firuzan. Firuzan is a popular nightclub performer who is eagerly working on an album as she leads a colorful but complicated life. When Firuzan meets Huseyin, the course of events gives away to a hilarious adventure.","poster_path":"/cXRQLlxt7FMOy